*Odustati* se od svega što je loše (To give up on all that is bad). 

Neću *odustati* od svojih ciljeva (I will not give up on my goals). 

*Odustajanje* od njihovih obećanja je bilo neizbežno (Their renouncement of their promises was inevitable). 

Ona se nikada neće *odustati* od svojih principa (She will never give up on her principles). 

Ne mogu *odustati* od svojih snova (I can't give up on my dreams). 

*Odustati* od borbe je bila njegova najveća greška (Giving up on the fight was his biggest mistake).